    "description": "Startia Holdings,Inc. engages in the IT business in Japan and internationally. The company offers digital marketing SaaS products and services comprising marketing automation tools, application creation software, web production and content management system, other digital marketing tools, AR creation software, and document management and e-book creation software that focuses on small and medium-sized enterprise market. It also provides IT infrastructure products and services, including total support service, copier / multifunction machine, business phone, network construction/maintenance, electricity, optical line / provider, web production / promotion, cloud construction/maintenance, office design, flat-rate printer, office relocation, security camera, commercial air conditioner, LED, air cleaner, and electronic breaker to medium-sized companies. In addition, the company offers indirect operations, such as accounting management, and support operations comprising formulation of investment plans for funds and human resources, as well as engages in discovering, executing, and managing investment projects primarily in Southeast Asia. Startia Holdings,Inc. was formerly known as Startia, Inc. and changed its name to Startia Holdings,Inc. in April 2018. Startia Holdings,Inc. was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Tokyo, Japan."
